title: Octi Evil/Geshundfight
description: Octi Evil: The heinous Him toys with Bubbles' mind by speaking to her through Octi, her favorite stuffed animal. Following Him's orders, Bubbles picks a fight with her sisters that lands them all in a time-out./Geshundfight: The Amoeba Boys' ill-conceived plan to stand in Townsville Park all night in the rain leaves them with a nasty virus that's really something to sneeze at.

title: Baile en La Plaza
description: Cuando Rad organiza su propia fiesta de graduación en la Plaza, K.O. intenta asegurarse de que no haya ninguna complicación.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Cuidado con el espantapajaros
description: Durante una visita a la granja del abuelo de Penny Bennyson, un espantapájaros que cobró vida gracias a Aristocuervo persigue constantemente al equipo Tennyson.

title: Juego tenebroso
description: Últimamente, la noche semanal de juegos de mesa de la banda se volvió demasiado competitiva, así que cuando Unikitty encuentra un viejo y espeluznante juego de mesa que claramente está embrujado, los deseos de ganar del grupo quedan dados vuelta, pero con o sin embrujo, iquieren ser los primeros en cruzar la línea de llegada!

title: Wiggin' Out
description: Bridgette donates her hair to a charity that makes wigs for hairless cats and now some classmates want to do the same. But their quest for perfect wig hair drives them to weird and dangerous lengths.

title: Terror Tales of the Park IV
description: The park guys try to keep Muscle Man awake with scary stories on a long drive so that they can meet his mom.

title: Back to the Kindergarten
description: Steven, Amethyst and Peridot try to spruce up the Kindergarten.

title: Manzana es Bajito
description: Manzana tiene que ser alto para poder enamorarse.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet The Thunderkittens
description: The Thunderkittens might be the youngest Thundercats, but Wilykit and Wilykat are a dynamic brother and sister duo! They'll help take down any foe, even if they don't really know what their own capsule weapons can do.

title: Silent Strike Part 2
description: Megatron tries desperately to prevent The Other One from entering their universe.

title: The Squashening
description: To escape a monster, the girls have to tell him a scary story.

title: Enemigos en el Aire
description: Cuando Los Fantásticos transportan la Célula Núcleo a las instalaciones de AAAnimus, son atacados por Masato Kazami y sus Guardaespaldas.

title: Little Homeschool
description: Welcome to Little Homeschool, a place on earth where Gems from all over the universe can come learn how to live together peacefully! But there's one Gem who refuses to attend.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Fire in the Hole
description: Duncan cooks up a nuclear hot sauce to mess with Chef, but accidentally summons Terry Spice, King of the Underworld!

title: Princess Monster Wife
description: When Ooo's princesses start losing body parts left and right, Finn and Jake investigate.

title: Two Lies, One Truth
description: As Lloyd unmasks Mystake for who she truly is, Emperor Garmadon embraces Harumi as his daughter of darkness. Meanwhile, Wu holds onto faith as he leads his friends into dangerous Oni territory in the hope of finding Firstbourne's nest

title: The Flower
description: When Gumball sees Leslie with Penny, he is overcome with uncontrollable jealousy.

title: Terror Tales of the Park II
description: The park can be a very scary place at night.

title: Bluebird
description: Steven questions the motives of a mysterious fusion that suddenly shows up at his house.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: La Batalla Decisiva
description: Luego de que la Célula Núcleo pusiera en estado de hibernación a los Bakugan de ambos equipos, Dan y Magnus se encuentran atrapados en una batalla donde lo apostarán todo.

title: Witch's Crew
description: On Halloween Night, Morbucks summons a monster that she didn't expect.

title: He's the Sheriff
description: The gang struggles to get rid of the King when he joins them as their new deputy-for-a-day!

title: Letters to Lars
description: Steven writes about the latest news of Beach City.

title: Fantasticos vs. AAAnimus Parte 2
description: Los Fantásticos unen fuerzas con Benton Dusk para rescatar a sus Bakugan y liberar la energía de la Célula Núcleo que AAAnimus tiene bajo su control.

title: Terror Tales of the Park III
description: Each of the park guys want to win a bet by telling the scariest story at a Halloween party.

title: Fantasticos vs. AAAnimus Parte 1
description: Los Fantásticos planean infiltrarse a AAAnimus para rescatar a sus Bakugan, pero Benton los detiene para ofrecerles un plan alternativo.

title: Todos quieren a rad
description: Cuando Rad postea un nuevo video que se vuelve viral, intenta sacarles jugo a sus 15 minutos de fama.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Under a Red Sun
description: Steppenwolf "boom tubes" Superman to a planet with a red sun in order to make the Man of Steel powerless. Somehow Batman and Big Barda have to locate the planet before Superman is destroyed.

title: Salvando a Faith
description: Lloyd y su equipo planean tomar el control del Oni Titan. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, los Ninja caen en las garras del Barón de Hierro y un viejo maestro regresa.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Silent Strike Part 1
description: Optimus and the Autobots infiltrate Decepticon Territory to destroy the Dark Matrix Megatron stole from a mysterious bot known only as "The Other One."

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Escuela De Payasos
description: Mientras Ben disfruta en el estacionamiento a la salida de un partido de fútbol americano de ex estudiantes de la Universidad de State, se alía con los antiguos compañeros del Abuelo Max para impedir que Zombozo, un payaso demente, le robe a todo el público durante el entretiempo.

title: Green Destiny
description: The Ninja finally return home and unite to stop Emperor Garmadon, forcing Lloyd to make a decision that will forever change Ninjago.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Witches Brew
description: The Titans throw a Halloween party and invite the Justice League but the witches brew Robin creates has side effects.

title: Apple's Short
description: Apple needs to be tall so that he can be in love.

title: Ghostfreaked Out
description: Ben's internal demons get externalized when Ghostfreak escapes from his watch and becomes a full fledged being on his own. The renegade alien then realizes he needs to meld with Ben's DNA in order to survive.

title: Rebelion En La Granja
description: Ben encuentra el laboratorio secreto del Doctor Ánimo -ahora gobernado por los alfas, sus mutantes superiores- y debe ayudar a los animales inferiores mientras está atrapado en forma de Insectoide.

title: Lessons for a Master
description: When Iron Baron forces Wu to retrieve the Dragon Armor, things don't go as planned. In Ninjago, Lloyd can only endure so much as he holds onto hope for the Ninjas' return.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: El Silbon
description: Víctor arma un laberinto de maíz embrujado, pero los chicos del pueblo creen que es muy malo. Vic decide hacer que el laberinto sea más aterrador con la ayuda de El Silbón para asustar de verdad a los chicos, pero El Silbón tiene sus propios planes.

title: Afraid of the Dark
description: When UG helps a little girl who is afraid of the dark, he convinces her there's nothing to be afraid of but their imaginations.  But when their imaginations prove to be pretty terrifying, they go on a quest to turn on the lights.

title: Scary Tales
description: During the gang's Halloween party, Unikitty discovers Brick isn't scared of anything! To get him in the holiday spirit, the gang tell their own ideas of what a spooky story is, hoping to scare the emotionless Rick for once, with each tale even scarier (and sillier) than the last!

title: Face Your Fears
description: Apple and Onion must face their fears while trapped in a pet shop, so they can save French Fry from facing hers.

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: Gathering Dark
description: Axel must help Bearbarian overcome his secret fear of the dark to stop Dynamo from stealing his ride.

title: Dweller in the Depths Part 1
description: When a mysterious shark-bot named Hammerbyte kidnaps comatose Windblade, Bee and Chromia must chase him into the depths of the Argon Sea to retrieve her.

title: Belson's Sleepover
description: Belson invites Clarence and friends to a sleepover party, with a catch: whoever can survive the night's pranks and scares will win Belson's old Acedia game system!

title: El Secreto del Lobo
description: El Emperador de Hielo despierta a una bestia gigante para que ataquea Lloyd y a su fiel compañero.

title: Bienvenidos al Inframundo Parte 2
description: Después de que Vic pierde una pelea de lucha libre, V&V viajan al inframundo para buscar el consejo de su tío, un famoso luchador llamado El Toro.

title: The Other One Part 2
description: The Other One reveals himself as an all-powerful Megatron from a universe where Optimus Prime is no more.

title: Everybody Likes Rad?
description: When Rad posts a video that goes viral, he tries to milk his 15 minutes of fame.

title: Goat!
description: Prohyas becomes obsessed with riding an uncooperative goat to get over a mountain.

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Scared Silly
description: When the Rust Bucket runs out of gas on a foggy East Coast road, Ben, Gwen and Max are forced to stay at a hotel being menaced by Creepy Carl, a local folklore expert, who may actually be a ghost!

title: Too Much Is Never Enough
description: Envious of Namagem's ability to wield more than three powers at a time, Mega Man tries taking all of his replicated schematics on board, with grave side effects.

title: Losing Ice
description: Feeling unappreciated, Ice Bear leaves his brothers to be the chef of a restaurant. Desperate to fill the void, Grizz and Panda look for Ice Bear's replacement.

title: Un Nuevo Empleo
description: Durante un comercial para celebrar su contrato con el equipo AAAnimus, Dan y Los Fantásticos deciden rebelarse antes que traicionar sus principios.

title: Clarence the Movie
description: When Clarence starts to play around with his home video camera, he becomes increasingly drawn into the world of filmmaking. From talking toys, to real actors, to documentary subjects, Clarence is determined to find the right style to tell his story!

title: Birthday Bash/Too Pooped to Puff
description: Birthday Bash: It's the girls birthday and some special presents have arrived from the girls' main enemies. Can they destroy these evil gifts without destroying their party?/Too Pooped to Puff: The girls become exhausted when the town begins to over use them. They go on strike and end up teaching the townspeople how to fend for themselves.

title: The Other One Part 1
description: The Other One and his Super Soldiers arrive, forcing Optimus and Megatron to fight together.

title: The Return
description: Ghostfreak has returned! And he has brought a Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein like aliens with him to help him shroud the Earth in darkness.

title: Trick or Creek
description: It's Halloween at the Creek, and Craig is on a mission to collect as much candy as humanly possible, but a spooky ghoul from the Creek's past threatens his haul.

title: TV Knight 5
description: Batman pretends to be sick to avoid work so he and Commissioner Gordon can run around town watching their favorite shows.

title: Dos mentiras una verdad
description: Cuando Lloyd desenmascara y revela la identidad de Mystake, el Emperador Garmadon acepta a Harumi como su hija de la oscuridad. Mientras tanto, Wu se aferra a su fe al llevar a sus amigos hacia territorios Oni peligrosos esperando encontrar el nido de la Primogénita.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Spoooooky Game
description: The gang's weekly board game night has been getting a little too competitive lately, so when Unikitty finds a spooky old board game that's clearly haunted, their desire to win gets turned upside down, but cursed or not, they'll be the first to the finish line!

title: Home, Sweet Homesick
description: When the Girls go to Camp, Blossom has a hard time leaving her schoolwork at home.

title: Consejos
description: Amatista ha estado ayudando a las Gemas de Pequeña Escuela Madre a encontrar trabajo, pero Steven no está seguro de su enfoque.

title: Yard Sale
description: Each of the Bears get offbeat items at a local yard sale. Their new possessions send them on their own separate adventures.

title: Boogie Frights/Abracadaver
description: Boogie Frights: The Boogie Man creates perpetual night by launching a huge disco ball to block out the sun. While evil creatures are dancing and destroying in the dark, the Powerpuff Girls plot to crash the ball./Abracadaver: Al Lusion, the old-time Townsville magician, pulls off his greatest stunt yet when he comes back from the dead as the zombie Abracadaver to haunt Townsville.

title: The Very Best Candy
description: The gang can't decide which of their candy is the best, so they turn it sentient and have it fight to determine the winner.

title: Destino verde
description: Los Ninjas regresan por fin a casa y se unen para detener al Emperador Garmadon, obligando a Lloyd a tomar una decisión que cambiará por siempre a Ninjago.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: The Frogs of War Part 1
description: The Incursean Armada, with the help of Dr. Psychobos, have invaded the Earth. (Reintroducing old Ben alien, BenMummy.)
